Certiorari Granted — Vacated and Remanded

No. 74-1162. Impson v. United States.

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari granted, judgment vacated, and case remanded for further consideration in light of United States v. Hale, ante, p. 171. Mr. Justice Douglas took no part in the consideration or decision of this case. Reported below: 506 F. 2d 1055.
